\label{fig:ber}
\end{figure}

\subsubsection{Training Convergence}

Figure 3 compares the training convergence of ComplexUNet and RealUNet. Both models achieve similar validation NMSE (~-16 dB) and converge within 150-170 epochs. The comparable training dynamics suggest that the Quantum Phase Rotation Gate does not significantly impact learning efficiency, despite adding architectural complexity.

